  <brief_title>Effect of Ile-Pro-Pro (IPP) on Endothelial Function in Patients With Coronary Artery Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Protein Hydrolysate Rich in Lacto-tripeptide (IPP) on Hyperemic Blood Flow and Flow-mediated Dilation in Patients With Coronary Artery Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
